---
title: Lentil and Beyond Meat® Cottage Pie with Mushrooms
description: This hearty bowl provides all the comfort of cottage pie without the finicky assembly. Protein-packed Beyond Meat®, lentils and savoury mushrooms are a satisfying and wholesome swap for the usual ground meat.
